  "description": "Weapon (Dagger), Rare\n\nYou gain a +1 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.\n\nYou can take a Bonus Action to magically coat the blade with poison. The poison remains for 1 minute or until an attack using this weapon hits a creature. That creature must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 2d10 Poison damage and have the &amp;Reference[Poisoned apply=false] condition for 1 minute. The weapon can't be used this way again until the next dawn.",
